Depolyment and compiling - tploader log parser

Author: Xie Di
Date: 2013.09.14
Version: 1.0.0

1. Depolyment

  a. Copy the parser and send_nsca binrary, send_nsca configuration and start script to proper directory.
  b. Run start script.

2. Compiling

  a. Change to src path.
  b. Run 'make' command.

3. Make options

linux               Create binary for linux platform.

aix                 Create binary for AIX platform.

debug               Print debug info to debug file.

no-precompile       Turns off lexer and grammar precompile.

4. Special Notes for AIX

  If no Flex and Bison is available, you could make on linux platform first, then go to AIX and type 'make aix no-precompile'.

